data.description: Don't let this beauty pass you by!! You will absolutely love this meticulously maintained home in this hidden gem 55+ community of Silver Lakes. Seller has ensured the home is in tip-top shape with the following upgrades installed in 2023: Generac 18+kw Generator for peace of mind, double-pane, energy-efficient, impact-resistant windows, oversize paver patio with natural stone curved seat wall, completed Florida room, new automatic garage door opener with new electric roll-up screen, gas tankless water heater, updated kitchen with new white cabinets, new backsplash, new granite countertops, new appliances, freshly painted interior of home on all surfaces, and January 2024 painted exterior of home. Re-roof completed in 2017. This is true Florida living that affords you to take full advantage of Silver Lakes lifestyle activities without having to worry about the cost of irrigation, cable/internet, or maintenance of the pool/clubhouse. Other features of this turn-key home are the split floor plan, pulldown stairs for attic access, crown molding, 40-yr Architectural Shingle Roof, security system, wheelchair accessible Jacuzzi tub in guest bath, walk-in shower with built-in seating in master bath, cedar-lined master closet, and 1.5-car garage. The clubhouse serves as a meeting point for all community related activities such as swimming pool, fitness center, sauna, billiards, library, arts and craft room, and multi-purpose room. Silver Lakes is a hidden gem and Lakeland's best kept secret; Silver Lakes allows for golf carts and is pet friendly! Easy access to I-4, shopping, and Lakeland's best Palace Italian Pizza. See you in Lakeland!
